Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on learning a forward model for a robot to plan and execute actions to achieve goals. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a machine learning approach to learn the forward model. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is relevant as the objects in the scene are represented by visual features. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes a learning-based approach to model the effects of actions. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also relevant as the paper discusses closed loop execution of action sequences.
